hon. Douglas Roche : 
honourable senators , I wish to address the eleventh report of the Standing Committee on Privileges , Standing Rules and Orders together with the ninth report of the same committee . 
honourable senators will be glad to know that even though I will speak about two reports , I will not speak for twice as long . 
