this is not some whim whereby some senator comes in here and says that he or she chooses to be independent because they do not wish to be this or that . 
the status is recognized in the appointment process . 
i believe , without belabouring this argument too much , that while it has a certain complexity to it , we must stand on the principle of full rights for independent senators . 
in that letter I applied for membership on two committees . 
